{"tid":2438060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"栗戰書：將完善香港選舉制度 打出一套法律「組合拳」","createTime":"2021-03-08T09:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T15:12:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fd888e03745cbab249f350d303dbee598274ea22","tid":2438060,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"第十三屆全國人民代表大會第四次會議在人民大會堂舉行第二次全體會議於今日下午三時舉行。人大常務委員會委員長栗戰書在會上發表工作報告，提及本次大會將作出關於完善香港選舉制度的決定，打出一套法律的「組合拳」。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，人大將堅定不移依法維護國家主權、安全、發展利益，為維護香港憲制秩序、打擊「港獨」勢力、確保愛國者治港、保持香港長期繁榮穩定提供法律保障。<br />\n<br />\n栗戰書又指，香港於2019年發生「修例風波」令法治和社會秩序遭遇嚴重衝擊，「一國兩制」受到嚴重挑戰，常委會於去年6月連續召開兩次會議，審議通過《港區國安法》，相關法律在港實施後，扭轉香港在國家安全領域長期「不設防」的嚴峻局面。"},{"pid":"3ba6f55b4379725b7d5cbf3b04d772364834a925","tid":2438060,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">全港人民中拳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d82956acc99cababef195f4e47239599fb2062","tid":2438060,"uid":255980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"咁佢以前係咪鐘意耍太極拳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />耍左香港人幾十年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3e2d976b0ac36ed67a2e421b97566fdfcc77ec","tid":2438060,"uid":134683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"極權統治下講既法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b362623f3dd82644625616b1f867b1e9449321","tid":2438060,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><